import React from "react";
import { Container, Typography, Paper, Grid, Card, CardContent, Box } from "@mui/material";

const AdminDashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 5 }}>
      <Paper
        elevation={4}
        sx={{
          p: 4,
          textAlign: "center",
          borderRadius: 2,
          backgroundColor: "#fff3e0", // Light orange background
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ mb: 3, fontWeight: "bold", color: "#e65100" }}>
          Admin Dashboard
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card
              sx={{
                border: "2px solid #e65100",
                borderRadius: 2,
                transition: "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s",
                "&:hover": {
                  transform: "scale(1.02)",
                  boxShadow: "0px 4px 12px rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.4)",
                },
              }}
            >
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: "#e65100", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
                    User Management
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Manage user accounts, permissions, and roles.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card
              sx={{
                border: "2px solid #e65100",
                borderRadius: 2,
                transition: "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s",
                "&:hover": {
                  transform: "scale(1.02)",
                  boxShadow: "0px 4px 12px rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.4)",
                },
              }}
            >
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: "#e65100", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
                    Test Management
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Oversee and manage tests, assessments, and evaluations.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card
              sx={{
                border: "2px solid #e65100",
                borderRadius: 2,
                transition: "transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s",
                "&:hover": {
                  transform: "scale(1.02)",
                  boxShadow: "0px 4px 12px rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.4)",
                },
              }}
            >
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: "#e65100", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
                    Analytics
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  View detailed analytics and insights for better decision making.
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default AdminDashboard;
